                                            gaming
                                            machines. In all the ways that matter, the sequel
                                            blueprint established in that well-loved release,
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="author_card_star star-rating">
                                        <span class="fa fa-star-o" data-rating="1"></span>
                                        <span class="fa fa-star-o" data-rating="2"></span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="author_card_link">
                                        <span>READ FULL REVIEW</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </li>

                            <li class="grading_li col-12 col-md-4">
